<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.8">
<l>vārpuṉa lantaṇ ṇaruvi vaṭatiru vēṅkaṭat tentai</l>
<l>pērpala collip pitaṟṟip pitta reṉṟē piṟarkūṟa</l>
<l>vūrpala pukkum pukātu mulōkar cirikka niṉṟāṭi</l>
<l>yārvam perukik kuṉippā ramarar toḻappaṭu vārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who chatter, saying many names of our father in sacred northern Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>with pretty cool waterfalls with overflowing floods, while others just say “madmen”,</l>
<l>entering and not entering many villages while those of the world laugh, who constantly dance</l>
<l>[and] bow, affection increasing, they will be worshipped by the immortals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
